			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Cotton is a seed-hair fibre of several species of plants of the genus Gossypium, belonging to the hibiscus, or mallow, family (Malvaceae). It is one of the world's leading agricultural crops, plentiful and economically produced. Cotton is a soft, fluffy staple fiber that grows in a boll, or protective case, around the seeds of the cotton plants. It is a staple textile of the fashion industry and the most widely produced natural fiber on the planet.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">棉花是属于木槿或锦葵科（锦葵属）的棉属植物中多个品种的籽毛纤维。它是世界主要农作物之一，产量丰富且经济实惠。棉花是一种柔软、蓬松的短纤维，生长在棉铃或棉花种子周围的保护壳中。它是时装业的主要纺织品，也是地球上生产最广泛的天然纤维。</common:generalComment>
